sections.content: The property covered under Gift Settlement Deed No. 436 of 2026, dated 29/Jan/2026, executed by Gunji Venkata Narasaiah in favour of his Wife, Gunji Jyothy, towards the property admeasuring an extent of 290.4 Sq. Yds., bearing house number 3-76/a Assessment No. 768, comprised in survey number 210/9, situated in Mallela Village and Gramapanchayat, Tiruvuru Mandal, Erstwhile Krishna District, now within the District of NTR, registered at sub-registrar office Tiruvuru is bounded as follows: North by: R & B Road South by: Property of Samsala Venkateswara Rao East by: Property of Gunji Venkaiah West by: Property of Akula Ramesh
It is noted from the given documents and EC that the schedule property is not part of any active Mortgage or Lease Deed.

Note It is to be noted that the online EC has been verified using the key parameters, namely the Document Number, Survey Number/House Number of the concerned SRO, as per the Deed. However, cross-verification across multiple SROs has not been carried out due to the AP portal’s requirement of separate passwords for each search parameter, and the OTP-based authentication mechanism makes searches across multiple SROs operationally infeasible
